To build the project, simply clone the recommender branch and compile with:
scalac -d bin src/*/*.scala

To execute the project with the mod5_342k.dat dataset use:
scala -cp bin main.Main datasets/mod5_342k.dat

The options -Dactors.corePoolSize=X -Dactors.maxPoolSize=X can be used to set the number of cores, where #Cores = X - 1.
You can find more information in our project report